FBIS4-18824 "drweu069_p_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-069 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 GREECE Arsenis Hopes For `No More' NATO Attacks Arsenis Hopes For `No More' NATO Attacks NC1104092994 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0900 GMT 11 Apr 94 NC1104092994 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] Referring to yesterday's attack in Bosnia-Herzegovina, National Defense Minister Yerasimos Arsenis expressed the hope that there will no more attacks by NATO. Arsenis described NATO and the United Nations as organizations not properly equipped to deal with situations like the crisis in Bosnia-Herzegovina. He also gave an assurance that he is following the situation closely.
